title: Do Sage Grouse Taste Like Sage Brush? I Drove 1,000 Miles To Hunt This Amazing Bird. Catch & Cook.

media:group.media:title: Do Sage Grouse Taste Like Sage Brush? I Drove 1,000 Miles To Hunt This Amazing Bird. Catch & Cook.
media:group.media:description:
Do Sage Grouse Taste Like Sage Bush? The Sage grouse is a very special game bird. I wanted to find out if the rumors are true about it tasting awful so I drove over 1000 miles round trip to hunt this special bird. I was not disappointed. In this video we cook an amazing recipe inspired by Hank Shaw's wild game cook book - Pheasant Quail Cottontail.
